    "body": "FIX: https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/issues/22363\n\nTested with:\n\n```\nVLLM_ATTENTION_BACKEND=TRITON_ATTN_VLLM_V1 vllm serve\n```\n\nand \n\n```\ncurl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/chat/completions      -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"      -d '{\n           \"model\": \"Qwen/Qwen3-0.6B\",\n           \"messages\": [\n             { \"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hello, vLLM!\" }\n           ],\n           \"max_tokens\": 50,\n           \"temperature\": 0.7\n}'\n```\n\ncredit to: @tjtanaa for the fix inspiration and notifying about the bug",
